Dadbot from HKIPGTD discord.

to run: 

* Set up bot configuration on discord and receive a bot token:
    https://github.com/jagrosh/MusicBot/wiki/Adding-Your-Bot-To-Your-Server

* Invite the bot to your own server:
    https://github.com/jagrosh/MusicBot/wiki/Adding-Your-Bot-To-Your-Server

* Create a file called settings.json and add the token to it. 'settings-example.json' is an example of such a file.    

* Run Mongo DB with docker-compose. In the given docker-compose.yml, the DB data will be kept in the 'dbstore' directory.:
    docker-compose up

* Install bot dependencies:
    npm install

* Run the bot:
    node ./app.js
